    "Id": "chassisdef_blue_flame_BLF-QSK",
    "Name": "Blue Flame",
    "Details": "Gotta go fast? We here at Quicksell have you covered with the blazing <i>Blue Flame</i>. Faster than even most light 'Mechs, the only thing that can outrun it is our Blue Hedgehog. Knowing that speedy 'Mechs often have issues tracking targets, we've packed a pair of LBX Lasers into the turret, providing a solid chance of connecting with any target you can see on the screen.\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Quirk: Stable Weapons</color></b>\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Drop Cost Multiplier: 1.03</color></b>",
